OL,3,CSir James Dyson named richest man in
OL,4,CSouth West
OL,6,FSir James Dyson has been named the
OL,7,Frichest man in the South West.
OL,9,FThe Sunday Times Rich List 2026 has
OL,10,Frevealed the wealthiest individuals
OL,11,Fand families in the UK, and how much
OL,12,Fthey are worth.
OL,14,FThe Wiltshire inventor came out on top
OL,15,Ffor the South West with an estimated
OL,16,Fwealth of #12 billion.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
