PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779120673
OL,3,CSir James Dyson named richest man in
OL,4,CSouth West
OL,6,FHe retains the top spot on the South
OL,7,FWest Rich List, despite a 13.5 per
OL,8,Fcent decline in revenues at Dyson's
OL,9,Fconsumer electricals group over the
OL,10,Fpast two years, partly due to Donald
OL,11,FTrump's tariffs.
OL,13,FProfits of #600 million have led to a
OL,14,Frevised valuation of #8 billion for
OL,15,Fthe Singapore-based business. A
OL,16,Ffurther #4 billion has been attributed
OL,17,Fto assets outside the company,
OL,18,Fincluding at least 36,000 acres of
OL,19,Ffarmland. Earlier this year, Sir James
OL,20,Falso acquired a 50 per cent stake in
OL,21,FBath Rugby.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
