PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779120673
OL,3,CSir James Dyson named richest man in
OL,4,CSouth West
OL,6,FFashion designer Jade Holland Cooper
OL,7,Fknown for her partnership with
OL,8,FCheltenham Festival also made the
OL,9,Flist, with an estimated #518 million.
OL,11,FGlastonbury's Emily Eavis was also
OL,12,Fnamed with an estimated wealth of #400
OL,13,Fmillion.
OL,15,FChris and Sarah Dawson, Peter
OL,16,FHargreaves, Douglas and Dame Mary
OL,17,FPerkins, Steve Lansdown, Lord Vestey,
OL,18,FJames Benamor, Nigel Spokes and Andrew
OL,19,FNisbet are also among the South West's
OL,20,Frichest.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
