OL,3,CSir James Dyson named richest man in
OL,4,CSouth West
OL,6,FThe number of billionaires recorded by
OL,7,Fthe list increased to 157 for the
OL,8,Fyear, nudging up from 156 a year ago
OL,9,Fafter a recent period of decline.
OL,11,FThese are the 20 richest people and
OL,12,Ffamilies in the UK, according to the
OL,13,FRich List:
OL,15,F1. Sanjay and Dheeraj Hinduja and
OL,16,Ffamily ` #38 billion
OL,18,F2. David and Simon Reuben and family `
OL,19,F#27.971 billion
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
