OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1779120673
OL,3,CSir James Dyson named richest man in
OL,4,CSouth West
OL,6,FFormer Manchester United star Sir
OL,7,FDavid Beckham has become Britain's
OL,8,Ffirst billionaire sportsman in the
OL,9,F2026 list ` but the club's co-owner
OL,10,FSir Jim Ratcliffe's wealth has
OL,11,Fdecreased over the last 12 months.
OL,13,FThis year's list of 350 individuals
OL,14,Fand families together holds combined
OL,15,Fwealth of #783.5 billion ` a sum
OL,16,Flarger than the annual GDP of Belgium
OL,17,F($776 billion), Sweden ($760 billion)
OL,18,Fand Israel ($719 billion). It
OL,19,Frepresents about a quarter of the
OL,20,FUnited Kingdom's total annual GDP.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
